{"tid":1861510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【民意調查】大家入左工會未？未入既講下咩原因","createTime":"2020-02-04T07:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T11:54:20.000Z","uid":27797,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"88b956ee452c121e70c56cfcf88a7bf63b1ef46c","tid":1861510,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:08:43.000Z","msg":"相信呢兩日醫護界罷工大家都見到加入工會對搞得成罷工既重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但希望大家唔好開心太早，我地仲未贏。過往罷工既經驗係，頭個一兩日幾係威係勢都好，如果對方唔理你一味拖，其實好難維持到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一旦社區爆發，醫護選擇番去救急扶危都無可厚非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以而家既重點係，大家唔可以將責任同期望都擺哂係醫護界度，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果個社會得醫護界出聲，其他人繼續一切如常，最多講聲醫護加油，呢場仗我地輸撚硬</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家而家要準備既係，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係醫護開始比人打壓既時候，其他各行各業可唔可以接力罷工</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然運輸業都開始籌備罷工，但係感覺個聲勢不如醫護，因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">醫護界當日係排哂隊入會話會罷工</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以好簡單，想做個民意調查，睇下日日講要罷工同醫護加油既連登仔入哂工會未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未入/無工會入/唔知入咩工會<br />\n<br />\n未入既係個post度講下咩原因，睇下有無人可以幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生就無你地既事，呢排咁得閒落去幫手擺街站撐醫護啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果真係唔知而家有咩工會既，可以睇下呢度：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ%2Fedit&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=efdb96db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋最後要講，係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">工會，工人個工，唔係公會呀！</span></strong></span>，唔知點解成日都見到有人打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31dabe607685e7ea465387cdcbf430563c2e7722","tid":1861510,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3f7ce002a17986b3c87147dbfff6b39b8495445b","tid":1861510,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"自推x2"},{"pid":"85e2c3491f1ffceb11277f4121748b38f9333f92","tid":1861510,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:13:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d5d71315c94f6ec8002920583a21d5b0574928d","tid":1861510,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:13:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef5958dfb607c24182484f7bb50db142e5ad9087","tid":1861510,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f5a6d94a76949ed1ccc5d88c78fa5a7cccdc153","tid":1861510,"uid":193364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88b956ee452c121e70c56cfcf88a7bf63b1ef46c","tid":1861510,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:08:43.000Z","msg":"相信呢兩日醫護界罷工大家都見到加入工會對搞得成罷工既重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但希望大家唔好開心太早，我地仲未贏。過往罷工既經驗係，頭個一兩日幾係威係勢都好，如果對方唔理你一味拖，其實好難維持到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fro