lyTime":"2020-02-04T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"公會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢半年用開ONLINE GAME TERM丫嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6374446862f11d8af49dbc0a724286edb5d305","tid":1861510,"uid":257368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"有冇測量師公會 搵左好多次都唔覺有"},{"pid":"8540f02058b62ded011ea9b21b9db9718d1f8763","tid":1861510,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"我諗會有d人會覺得自己做細公司，入唔入工會罷唔罷工都無所謂<br />\n但其實你加入行業工會（例如文職、物流業工會等等），唔洗理你間公司大定細，多一個人就多一份力，交多一份會費，罷工罷到有人被炒，就有多一份資源幫助手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n掉番轉，你唔入工會，到時有事你想幫手都未必幫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以入左先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d642ca79f463741b562bec501918f6cdebf6bf","tid":1861510,"uid":189499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"我搵過幾次 其實我做飲食業back office <br />\n我真係唔知自己符唔符合 入飲食業既公會"},{"pid":"2a6ea37afe664d8bd5ce86ca85ffaede568390c5","tid":1861510,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13d642ca79f463741b562bec501918f6cdebf6bf","tid":1861510,"uid":189499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"我搵過幾次 其實我做飲食業back office <br />\n我真係唔知自己符唔符合 入飲食業既公會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"Telegram 頻道： <a href=\"https://t.me/chiegubroadcast\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fchiegubroadcast&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=fe1c6fea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/chiegubroadcast</a><br />\n<br />\nTG光復飲食業group: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/N4A4d03zH1aIQCyuLQou2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FN4A4d03zH1aIQCyuLQou2w&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlPFnd